metadata.name: 2am in Amsterdam
metadata.description: On a trip to Amsterdam, I spent my time documenting this beautiful city. One of the many scenes I was able to capture was one of this couple who had just left a bar. They had been kissing each other passionately down the street but I couldnâ€™t seem to find the perfect moment to capture this. They then ducked down an alleyway and passionately continued kissing each other. The lighting and composition of the scene came together perfectly. Two lovers, totally engaged with each other as if nothing else in this world matters.
